In this range, each watch has a plain silicone strap with a patterned dial that contains either a butterfly or bird print in a range of different colours. This particular Ice-Watch has a bird print dial in colours of grey, white and orange. The dial measures approximately 38mm in width, this measurement includes the crown, the case depth is approximately 8mm and the strap length can be easily adjusted via the buckle which secures it in place. The buckle is a rich gold colour and this matches the crown, the hands on the dial as well as the Ice logo. The water resistant level of this watch is 100m so you can wear the watch whilst swimming. The durable silicone strap is perfect for everyday wear and is comfortable against the wrist. Each Ice-Watch comes with a two year manufacturer’s warranty and is sent in the official original branded packaging.
